                            b
                             .sub Let’s figure out a plan.
                        br
                        h4
                            b
    
                                a.slider__a(href="#") Learn more &#8594

                .carousel-item.py-5
                    h1.slider__tittle-mob On campus
                    img.slider__image.col-5(src='https://www.americanfunds.com/content/dam/cgc/shared-content/images/infographics/students-on-college-campus-graphic.png' alt='On campus')
                    article.col-lg-6.slider__article
                        h1.slider__tittle-desk On campus
                        p.lead With your child on campus, you need to stretch your money now and tackle how to handle the debt that’s coming later.
